[March 26th, 2020 2:04 PM] sefanittades: Hellooo, <!channel>! Please be prepared for an all hands call at 9:30am PDT / 12:30pm EDT / 7:30pm EAT tomorrow, 3/27.

We will be covering:
• New important documents & organizational processes to make all of our lives easier
• Progress so far with all our partners
• Projects in development across all workstreams
• Outreach for leads, moderators & any project-related assistance from members of our community
Gcal invites will be sent sometime this evening (<https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdYEaHBgkJpolgbrD3Y8ESbiDsx-WPY-S1j6hcNaq2KCthIBA/viewform|if you haven’t filled out the volunteer form, please do so here>). A zoom link, along with a link to the Agenda + Minutes will be provided at least 30mins prior, on this channel. We’ll do our best to do a recap here after the call as well, for all that cannot make it.

The purpose of this call is to help us all go into this weekend strong, & as productive as we can be.

Please stay healthy & let’s make real impact, folks! :woman-cartwheeling::skin-tone-4:

text:
Does any one know how we can get data to  enrich (to fill the null fields) in the geojson data located at <https://github.com/Ethiopia-COVID19/health-facilities-geojson/blob/master/hotosm_eth_health_facilities_points.geojson>? It would be nice if we can fill a subset of the existing fields and add the following:
• #ICU beds 
• #EC patients capacity 
• #total beds
• #EC specialists
• #doctors 
• #nurses
This data is most likely available in the MoH database or some other place, but I have no contact to check it out. Please DM if you have some idea.
